	   <tr><td colspan=2>The new bard songs are located in Katta Calleseum in Luclin. This is probably one of the not too smart moves of VI. Katta is isolated from other cities and is not a very safe journey to get to. Once you are there, you will find the SoL bard songs, well worth the trip...at least for Amplification.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
