<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=101137662310168></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f101137662310168><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=4&mid=101137662310168>Here's a great cheep weapon for those who aren't twinked.</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=4&mid=101137662310168#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=137128><span id= >TIRGA</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>1 posts</td></tr>
