	   <tr><td colspan=2>I found an exellent weapon for those bards still using their mino axes and such at low levels. Yes, a 8/30 MAGIC weapon can be yours for the low low price of 5 platinum (approx). This is how you get it.<br>If you have the SoL expansion go to the Vah Shir city, Shar Val, from there proceed through Hollowshade Moore, following the path across TWO bridges, it heads to your left. You will then pass into a cave that leads to the Grimling Forest, if you head RIGHT (Don't go left if you value your life) you will see a Vah shir encampment. In the back there is a merchant which sells 2 Weapons of which you might like: <br><br>Validus Custodus Long Sword&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>MAGIC ITEM  <br>Damage: 7<br>Delay: 27 <br>Ratio: 3.857 Good <br>Weight: 5.0 <br>Weapon Skill: One Hand Slash <br>Classes: Warrior Rogue Bard Shadowknight Paladin Ranger  <br>Races: All Races  <br> <br>MAGIC ITEM  <br>Damage: 8<br>Delay: 30 <br>Ratio: 3.75 Good <br>Weight: 8.5 <br>Weapon Skill: One Hand Slash <br>Classes: Warrior Rogue Bard Shadowknight Paladin Ranger  <br>Races: All Races  <br>Inventory Slot: Either Melee<br>Can be stored in Medium and larger containers <br><br>These are great weapons for the price. Maybe they had just been sold... but allot of people had bough them and they never dissapeared... sooo. Hope they are. Worth the trip.<br><br>Good luck to you all and may your song sound nothing but sweet!<br>&nbsp;<br>TIRGA<br>LEVEL 13 BARD OF FIRONIA VIE</td></tr>
