	   <tr><td colspan=2>Posting your level and financial possibilities would help a lot. Personally i think banded is a very good choice as upgrade for the leather pieces, its very cheap and has decent AC. Bronze is usually too heavy to be a useful alternative.<br>With the FP this should keep you in business till you can go for Lambent.<br><br>As far as weapons go, the Minotaur axe is not magical, so you'll have to use the new SOL song making your weapon magical to kill wisps which are very good money and exp.<br>I personally prefer piercing weapons, but that is mainly because my main handed down first a dragoon dirk (6/23) and then a crystalline spider fang (10/22). The dragoon dirk is affordable to a lower level (50pp), the fang is not (2500pp)<br>&nbsp;<br>Nindor<br>L52 Dwarven Cleric on Zebuxoruk</td></tr>
